**Funnel Metrics:**
- Landing page visitors
- Registration completion rate
- Onboarding drop-off points
- Payment initiation rate
- Payment abandonment rate
- Post-payment onboarding completion

**User Feedback:**
- Exit survey for non-converters
- NPS survey for enrolled users
- Support ticket themes
- Qualitative interviews (10 users)

**Technical Metrics:**
- API response times
- Webhook latency
- Email delivery rates
- DB query performance
- Error rates by endpoint

### 11.2 Deliverables

- Campaign performance report (metrics, trends)
- User feedback summary
- Technical incident log
- Recommendations for full platform launch
- Updated pricing strategy based on conversion data
- Marketing channel effectiveness analysis

