## 13. Appendix

### 13.1 Environment Variables Required

```bash
# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...
ENV=production  # triggers SQLite guard — REQUIRED in prod

# Auth
JWT_SECRET_KEY=...  # generate: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(32))"
SUPABASE_URL=...    # optional OAuth
SUPABASE_KEY=...
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=...
CLASSROOM_AUTH_MODE=strict

# Payment
MIDTRANS_MERCHANT_ID=...
MIDTRANS_CLIENT_KEY=...
MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY=...
MIDTRANS_ENV=sandbox|production
IDR_RATE=16000

# Email
EMAIL_PROVIDER=sendgrid|postmark|noop
SMTP_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USERNAME=apikey
SMTP_PASSWORD=...
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@vokasi.id

# Feature Flags
FF_HYBRID_ONBOARDING=true
FF_EMAIL_EVENTS=true

# AI
OPENAI_API_KEY=...
GEMINI_API_KEY=...
```

### 13.2 API Endpoints Summary

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Purpose |
|--------|----------|------|---------|
| POST | /api/v1/auth/register | None | Backend fallback registration |
| POST | /api/v1/auth/login | None | JWT login |
| GET | /api/v1/onboarding/profile | JWT | Get user onboarding profile |
| POST | /api/v1/onboarding/profile | JWT | Update onboarding profile |
| POST | /api/v1/onboarding/postpay-complete | JWT | Mark post-payment onboarding complete |
| GET | /api/v1/cohorts | None | List active cohorts |
| GET | /api/v1/cohorts/{slug} | None | Get cohort details + pricing |
| POST | /api/v1/cohorts/{slug}/initiate | JWT | Initiate Midtrans payment |
| POST | /api/v1/cohorts/{slug}/confirm | None (Midtrans signature) | Payment webhook |
